OL,3,CBrothers cleared of murdering couple
OL,4,Cat petrol station in 2003
OL,6,FTwo brothers who have spent almost 20
OL,7,Fyears in prison for a double murder
OL,8,Fthey say they didn't commit have
OL,9,Feffectively been cleared after a
OL,10,Fplanned retrial was cancelled.
OL,12,FLee and Robert Firkins were found
OL,13,Fguilty of the 2003 murders of Graham,
OL,14,F60 and Carol Fisher, 53 at their
OL,15,Fpetrol station in Perch near
OL,16,FWadebridge, in Cornwall.
OL,18,FThe men pleaded not guilty but were
OL,19,Fhanded life sentences with a minimum
OL,20,Fterm of 26 years in February 2006.
