OL,4,Cat petrol station in 2003
OL,6,FIn 2023, the Court of Appeal
OL,7,Foverturned the original conviction as
OL,8,Fa result of new medical evidence from
OL,9,Fthe Criminal Case Review Commission.
OL,11,FThe brothers were due to undergo a
OL,12,Fretrial in the early part of 2025, but
OL,13,Fthe Crown Prosecution Service has
OL,14,Fconcluded there is no longer a
OL,15,Frealistic prospect of conviction after
OL,16,Freviewing the available evidence.
OL,18,FDevon and Cornwall Police said work is
OL,19,Fongoing to manage the acquittal
OL,20,Fprocess. Robert Firkins has now been
OL,21,Freleased from prison.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
