OL,6,FLee Firkins will not be released due
OL,7,Fto other crimes he is serving
OL,8,Fsentences for, the force said.
OL,10,FA spokesperson for Devon and Cornwall
OL,11,FPolice said: "In 2023 the Court of
OL,12,FAppeal overturned the original
OL,13,Fconviction as a result of new medical
OL,14,Fevidence from the Criminal Case Review
OL,15,FCommission.
