OL,6,F"Since that point Devon and Cornwall
OL,7,FPolice's Major Crime Investigation
OL,8,FTeam has worked closely with the Crown
OL,9,FProsecution Service (CPS) to prepare
OL,10,Ffor a retrial of Robert and Lee
OL,11,FFirkins scheduled for early 2025.
OL,13,F"Devon and Cornwall Police accepts the
OL,14,FCPS has conducted a careful review of
OL,15,Favailable evidence in the case and
OL,16,Fhave concluded that there is no longer
OL,17,Fa realistic prospect of conviction.
OL,18,FConsequently, the CPS has decided not
OL,19,Fto present any evidence before the
OL,20,Fcourt.
