OL,6,F"Steps are already underway to manage
OL,7,Fthe acquittal process including the
OL,8,Frelease of Robert Firkins from prison.
OL,9,FLee Firkins will remain in custody due
OL,10,Fto other sentences he is currently
OL,11,Fserving.
OL,13,F"Devon and Cornwall Police understand
OL,14,Fthat whilst the original investigation
OL,15,Fwas over 20 years ago, it is possible
OL,16,Fthat new information exists and so
OL,17,Fanyone who wants to contact ourselves
OL,18,For Crimestoppers, should do so as soon
OL,19,Fas possible."
