OL,6,FLegal team say case should lead to
OL,7,F'legal reform'
OL,9,FThe legal team representing the
OL,10,FFirkins brothers have said the case
OL,11,Fwas a "gross miscarriage of justice"
OL,12,Fand should prompt "legal reform".
OL,14,FJames Wood KC and Sarah Elliott KC
OL,15,Fwere both part of the original defence
OL,16,Fteams representing the two brothers
OL,17,Faccused of the Fishers' murders.
OL,19,FThey said the case had been dependent
OL,20,Fon alleged "cell confession" evidence
OL,21,Fprovided by a prisoner witness.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
