OL,6,FJames and Sarah commented: "From the
OL,7,Fmoment of these convictions, we knew
OL,8,Fthe case was a gross miscarriage of
OL,9,Fjustice. Based on an alleged cell
OL,10,Fconfession, it illustrated the
OL,11,Finherent dangers of this kind of
OL,12,Fevidence.
OL,14,F"The time is now ripe for legal
OL,15,Freform. Without independent reliable
OL,16,Fevidence supportive of the fact of the
OL,17,Fconfession, cell confession evidence
OL,18,Fis so dangerous, it should always be
OL,19,Fexcluded. This reform is now long
OL,20,Foverdue."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
